53
00:02:31,510 --> 00:02:33,759
Dia melompat begitu aku muncul.

54
00:02:33,842 --> 00:02:35,550
Tapi dia ada di luar sana.

55
00:02:35,633 --> 00:02:37,049
Dia sudah di luar sana.

56
