Aku punya kabar buruk.

97
00:04:50,578 --> 00:04:53,493
Bukan soal cucuku. Soal teman.

98
00:04:54,493 --> 00:04:56,492
- Sulit dijelaskan.
- Lorena, Rebecca.

99
00:04:56,575 --> 00:04:58,283
Kalian selalu banyak bicara...

100
00:04:58,366 --> 00:05:00,032
Saat bersama.

101
00:05:01,157 --> 00:05:06,196
Hei. Dengar, jika perlu bicara
soal apa pun, aku di sini.

102
